cdata.name: EXTRADECOIN
cdata.desc:
Extradecoin is a blockchain-based trading platform aiming for the improvement of the trading quality, reliability and safety-ness. The Extradecoin exchange offers 2FA security system, Multisignature Wallet, margin trading, token-play (Worms Armageddon, Dice Game, Diamond Game and Kitty Meow) and the ability to buy ICO tokens listed on the platform.

The ETE token is an Ethereum-based ERC20 token used as a payment method within the Extradecoin ecosystem.
